Dialogue: 55,0:01:56.43,0:01:58.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Look behind him!
Dialogue: 55,0:01:58.97,0:02:00.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A rainbow! There's a rainbow!
Dialogue: 55,0:02:03.56,0:02:05.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Even the way he cries is big!
Dialogue: 55,0:02:05.65,0:02:07.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's practically a waterfall!
Dialogue: 55,0:02:07.98,0:02:10.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel,\NMaster Brogy!
Dialogue: 55,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Dorry! How are you...?
Dialogue: 55,0:02:33.72,0:02:36.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It seems I blacked out.
Dialogue: 55,0:02:39.39,0:02:41.43,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Mr. 0?
Dialogue: 55,0:02:42.27,0:02:47.40,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Wasn't Mr. 0 the name of the enemy boss Vivi-chan talked about? - OG}Wasn't "Mr. 0" the name\Nof the enemy boss Vivi mentioned?
Dialogue: 55,0:02:48.23,0:02:52.36,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/q2]Which means the guy on the other end\Nof this transponder snail... - OG}Which means the guy I'm talking to\Non this transponder snail...{Z}
Dialogue: 55,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.45,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}is one of the Seven Warlords of the Sea?!
Dialogue: 55,0:03:00.45,0:03:04.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's been many days\Nsince I issued your orders. - OG}I issued your orders several days ago.
Dialogue: 55,0:03:04.37,0:03:06.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What's going on? - OG}What in the world is going on?{Z}
Dialogue: 55,0:03:06.29,0:03:08.38,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Mr. 3... - OG}It says "Mr. 3."
Dialogue: 55,0:03:08.38,0:03:11.25,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,So he's the owner\Nof this transponder snail?
Dialogue: 55,0:03:12.55,0:03:15.38,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{I think I got it figured out now. - OG}It's all coming together now.{Westfal}
Dialogue: 55,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.01,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,This is an enemy hideout,
Dialogue: 55,0:03:17.01,0:03:22.06,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{and a guy named Mr. 3 came\Nto the island to take Vivi-[/i1]chan[/i0]'s life. - OG}and a guy named Mr. 3\Ncame to the island to take Vivi's life.
Dialogue: 55,0:03:22.68,0:03:24.77,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 55,0:03:24.77,0:03:27.69,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{This was no time\Nfor me to be hunting! - OG}I wasted all this time hunting!{Gaijin/Sil}
Dialogue: 55,0:03:27.69,0:03:29.81,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{I hope they're all okay! - OG}I hope everyone's okay!
Dialogue: 55,0:03:31.27,0:03:33.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Why the silent treatment?
Dialogue: 55,0:03:33.90,0:03:36.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I asked you a question.
Dialogue: 55,0:03:36.45,0:03:40.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have you eliminated Princess Vivi\Nand the Straw Hats?!
Dialogue: 55,0:03:40.62,0:03:43.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, mission complete! - OG}Yeah, mission accomplished!{Westfal}
Dialogue: 55,0:03:43.16,0:03:47.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I got rid of everyone\Nwho found out about your secret. - OG}I got rid of everyone\Nwho knew your secret.
Dialogue: 55,0:03:47.75,0:03:50.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So there's no need\Nto go after 'em anymore. - OG}This means we can call off the dogs.{Z}
Dialogue: 55,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I see. Well done.
Dialogue: 55,0:03:53.13,0:03:56.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,As we speak, the Unluckies\Nare headed your way
Dialogue: 55,0:03:56.26,0:04:00.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{to confirm your mission is complete\N[/i1]and[/i0]to deliver a certain package. - OG}to verify the mission's accomplishment\N{\i1}and{\i0} to deliver a certain package.{Z/Sil}
Dialogue: 55,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Unluckies? Package?
Dialogue: 55,0:04:02.93,0:04:06.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,An eternal pose that points\Nto the Kingdom of Alabasta.
Dialogue: 55,0:04:08.10,0:04:13.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You and Miss Golden Week\Nwill head to Alabasta. - OG}You and Miss Golden Week\Nwill need to make your way there.{Z/Westfal}
Dialogue: 55,0:04:13.73,0:04:15.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The time has come.
Dialogue: 55,0:04:15.11,0:04:19.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We're about to begin our\Nmost important operation. - OG}We will commence our\Nmost critical operation to date.{Gaijin/PJ}
Dialogue: 55,0:04:19.61,0:04:23.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Details will come after you reach\NAlabasta. Wait for my orders. - OG}Once in Alabasta,\Nawait further orders.
Dialogue: 55,0:04:26.83,0:04:28.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What are these things?! - OG}Who the hell are these guys?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 55,0:04:32.59,0:04:34.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey! What's going on?! - OG}Hey. What's the problem?{\i0}
Dialogue: 55,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Oh, it's nothing... - OG}Oh, no worries. It's noth–
Dialogue: 55,0:04:39.01,0:04:40.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 55,0:04:56.19,0:04:57.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You tryin' to kill me?! - OG}You wanna kill me?!{Z/Sil}
Dialogue: 55,0:04:57.74,0:05:00.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bring it on, you damn monkey!
Dialogue: 55,0:05:07.04,0:05:08.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm telling you... - OG}How about you...{Z}
Dialogue: 55,0:05:12.38,0:05:14.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{to stop that! - OG}{to cut that out, - Z}give it a rest,{Z}
Dialogue: 55,0:05:14.75,0:05:16.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You jumbo-sized chicken! - OG}you oversized chicken!
Dialogue: 55,0:05:21.80,0:05:24.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was that?! What happened?!
Dialogue: 55,0:05:24.55,0:05:28.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Oh, uhh, no! It ain't- \NI mean, it's nothing! - OG}Oh, i-it's nothing. Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 55,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That damn Straw Hat was still alive.
Dialogue: 55,0:05:31.81,0:05:36.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,960)}It's okay, though. I finished him off.\NNo need to worry.
Dialogue: 55,0:05:37.53,0:05:39.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Still alive?
Dialogue: 55,0:05:40.49,0:05:43.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You just said your mission\Nwas complete... - OG}You told me "mission accomplished."{Gaijin/Westfal}
Dialogue: 55,0:05:43.91,0:05:45.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Did you not? - OG}Didn't you?
Dialogue: 55,0:05:47.33,0:05:49.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yes, well... - OG}Well, yes.
Dialogue: 55,0:05:49.62,0:05:51.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I thought it was complete... - OG}I thought it was, y'know?
Dialogue: 55,0:05:52.54,0:05:56.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But he was much tougher\Nthan you'd believe... - OG}But that bastard was a lot\Ntougher than you'd imagine.{Z}
Dialogue: 55,0:05:56.92,0:06:02.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{In other words...\Nthe report you gave me was a lie. - OG}In other words, what you\Ngave me was a false report.
Dialogue: 55,0:06:02.97,0:06:07.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Umm, well... I suppose so,\Nwhen you put it that way... - OG}Um, well... I suppose\Nthat's what it sounds like.
Dialogue: 55,0:06:07.72,0:06:10.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But I've gotten rid\Nof him for sure now. - OG}{But I stamped him out\Nfor good now. - Z}But he won't be\Ncoming back from this one.{Z}
Dialogue: 55,0:06:10.85,0:06:13.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So there's no need to send\Nany more after 'em. Okay? - OG}So, no need to send\Nanyone else. Capisce?
Dialogue: 55,0:06:14.48,0:06:15.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Very well. - OG}Enough.
Dialogue: 55,0:06:15.73,0:06:20.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Just head straight\Nto Alabasta from there now! - OG}You're to head straight\Nto Alabasta immediately!
Dialogue: 55,0:06:24.24,0:06:27.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's probably...\Nbecause of the weapons... - OG}It must've been...\Ndue to the weapons.
Dialogue: 55,0:06:27.12,0:06:29.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The weapons?! Oh, yeah! - OG}The weapons?! Of course!
Dialogue: 55,0:06:30.41,0:06:33.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Not even Elbaph weapons\Ncould keep up with two giants - OG}{These weapons,\Nthough forged in Elbaph,}Not even weapons forged in Elbaph
Dialogue: 55,0:06:33.33,0:06:37.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{fighting to the death\Nfor 100 years straight! - OG}{are completely worn out after a century-long duel between giants! - Z}could withstand a century-long\Nduel between giants!
Dialogue: 55,0:06:39.13,0:06:40.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Talk about crazy... - OG}Of all the crazy luck...
Dialogue: 55,0:06:41.51,0:06:42.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's a huge miracle! - OG}What a miracle!
Dialogue: 55,0:06:44.76,0:06:48.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Brogy! Don't hold on to me!\NThat hurts my wounds! - OG}{Hey, Brogy! Don't clutch me!\NIt upsets my wounds! - Gaijin}Hey, Brogy! Quit squeezing!\NYou'll open my wounds!{Westfal}
Dialogue: 55,0:06:49.26,0:06:52.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm so glad you're alive,\Nfriend of mine! - OG}I'm so glad you're alive, old friend!
Dialogue: 55,0:06:57.61,0:07:00.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Miracle, my ass. It's only natural. - OG}What miracle?\NThis was bound to happen.
Dialogue: 55,0:07:00.98,0:07:05.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The fact those weapons are still intact after 100 years of constant bashing and clanging is even crazier. - OG}{What's crazy is those weapons remain intact despite the punishment they took. - Gaijin}{\q2}After 100 years of clashing and clanging,\Nit's crazier that those weapons are still intact.{Z}
Dialogue: 55,0:07:05.70,0:07:07.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{As are their owners. - OG}Not to mention their owners.
Dialogue: 55,0:07:07.20,0:07:10.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What a wonderful day today is! - OG}This is truly a glorious day!
Dialogue: 55,0:07:10.58,0:07:12.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I thank you, God of Elbaph! - OG}I give thanks to the gods of Elbaph!
Dialogue: 55,0:07:13.12,0:07:14.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh, Brogy?
Dialogue: 55,0:07:14.50,0:07:20.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\t(16,975,1,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}{\t(5063,0,1,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}{Was chopping me down and knocking\Nme out that happy for you? - OG}{\q2}So cutting me down and taking me out\Nwas a joyous occasion?{Gaijin, per our discussion, this might be a bad translation.}
Dialogue: 55,0:07:20.92,0:07:24.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You dimwit!\NThat ain't what I'm saying! - OG}You numbskull!\NYou have the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 55,0:07:24.22,0:07:27.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Ow! Don't touch my wounds! - OG}Ouch! Watch out for my wounds!
Dialogue: 55,0:07:37.56,0:07:38.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You want some of this?! - OG}You want some more?!
Dialogue: 55,0:07:38.90,0:07:42.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah! I'll wipe the floor with ya! - OG}Yeah! I'll drop you again!
Dialogue: 55,0:07:43.40,0:07:48.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cool! Cool! Cool! Cool!
Dialogue: 55,0:07:49.41,0:07:51.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Why are you guys fighting again?! - OG}Why are you guys at it again?!
Dialogue: 55,0:07:52.49,0:07:56.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And no further radio\Ncontact from now on. - OG}{And you will practice\Nstrict radio silence. - Z}From here on out,\Npractice radio silence.{Westfal}
Dialogue: 55,0:07:56.71,0:07:59.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We don't want the Marines\Ncatching whiff of us. - OG}It'll keep the Marines\Nfrom catching on to us.
Dialogue: 55,0:08:00.38,0:08:05.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{All further orders will be sent\Nvia letter, as usual. - OG}{From here on, you'll only receive\Nwritten orders, as in the past. - Z}All further orders will be sent\Nin writing, as per usual.{Z}
Dialogue: 55,0:08:05.17,0:08:08.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That is all. Good luck, Mr. 3.
Dialogue: 55,0:08:16.31,0:08:18.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Miss All-Sunday.
Dialogue: 55,0:08:20.19,0:08:20.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 55,0:08:20.98,0:08:24.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Send Mr. 2 to Little Garden. - OG}Have Mr. 2 head to Little Garden.
Dialogue: 55,0:08:26.28,0:08:31.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Eliminate Mr. 3 on his direct course\Nto Alabasta from Little Garden. - OG}{On his way to Alabasta from Little Garden,\NMr. 3 needs to disappear. - Z}{\q2}Mr. 3 will meet his demise\Nen route to Alabasta from Little Garden.
Dialogue: 55,0:08:32.24,0:08:36.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's quite aggressive, sir.\NMr. 0, Crocodile. - OG}How cold-blooded of you,\NSir "Mr. 0" Crocodile.
Dialogue: 55,0:08:37.12,0:08:39.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We have enough manpower as it is.
Dialogue: 55,0:08:39.75,0:08:42.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Are you arguing with me? - OG}Are you questioning my decision?{Z}
Dialogue: 55,0:08:42.33,0:08:44.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No, I'll do as you wish.
Dialogue: 55,0:08:44.55,0:08:46.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'll make arrangements at once.
Dialogue: 55,0:08:50.05,0:08:51.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Well, he's hung up. - OG}Well, he hung up.
Dialogue: 55,0:08:51.68,0:08:52.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So, let's see... - OG}Let's see...{Z}
Dialogue: 55,0:08:53.26,0:08:56.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What were these guys, anyway?! - OG}Just who were these guys?
Dialogue: 55,0:09:02.56,0:09:03.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What do we have here? - OG}What's this?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 55,0:09:05.36,0:09:07.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Captain Smoker! Captain Smoker!
Dialogue: 55,0:09:07.61,0:09:09.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I've just intercepted\Nan intriguing signal! - OG}{\q2}We intercepted an intriguing transmission.
Dialogue: 55,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 55,0:09:14.49,0:09:17.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What an incredible full temper!
Dialogue: 55,0:09:17.04,0:09:18.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The fine grade sword, Kashu!
Dialogue: 55,0:09:19.62,0:09:21.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tashigi! Hey, Tashigi!
Dialogue: 55,0:09:21.67,0:09:26.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Only in the Grand Line could I\Nfind a legendary named sword so quickly! - OG}Only on the Grand Line can you\Nfind a named blade so readily!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 55,0:09:26.88,0:09:28.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tashigi! Hey!
Dialogue: 55,0:09:28.26,0:09:30.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Are you deaf, you sword freak?!
Dialogue: 55,0:09:30.30,0:09:31.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!{Z - I know we just talked about "Yes sir" going without a comma, but the accepted written form seems to be with a comma.}
Dialogue: 55,0:09:31.26,0:09:33.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What is it, Captain Smoker?!\NIs coffee– - OG}What is it, Captain Smoker?!\NThe coffee is–
Dialogue: 55,0:09:38.68,0:09:42.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Just get over here and listen with us! - OG}Just get over here and listen to this!
Dialogue: 55,0:09:43.69,0:09:47.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Listen close. We just picked up\Nthis conversation between two men.
Dialogue: 55,0:09:47.61,0:09:49.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Ready, Chief Petty Officer.\NHere we go. - OG}Are you ready, Chief?\NLet's play it back.
Dialogue: 55,0:09:49.57,0:09:51.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Y-Yes. Please play it back. - OG}Y-Yes. If you would.
Dialogue: 55,0:09:53.57,0:09:54.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...'s me. Mr. 0.
Dialogue: 55,0:09:55.45,0:09:57.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Princess Vivi and the Straw Ha...
Dialogue: 55,0:09:58.79,0:10:01.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Straw Ha...? The Straw Hat Pirates!
Dialogue: 55,0:10:01.00,0:10:03.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Yeah, mission complete! - OG}Yeah, mission accomplished!{Westfal}
Dialogue: 55,0:10:04.67,0:10:08.42,Main-207-,,0,0,10,,{\i1}{further orders... \Nvia letter, as usual... - OG}{...you'll only...\Nwritten orders, as in the past. - Z}...further orders will...\Nin writing, as per usual.{Z}{Rewritten line of origin @08:04: All further orders will be sent\Nin writing, as per usual.}
Dialogue: 55,0:10:08.42,0:10:10.13,Main-207-,,0,0,10,,{\i1}That is all. Good luck...
Dialogue: 55,0:10:11.80,0:10:14.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The rest is indecipherable.
Dialogue: 55,0:10:14.30,0:10:20.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's a faint signal, but there are four keywords in their conversation: - OG}The signal was faint, but we made out\Nfour keywords in this conversation:
Dialogue: 55,0:10:20.72,0:10:26.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Princess Vivi; Straw Hat;\NOrders via letter; and Mr. 0. - OG}Princess Vivi; Straw Hat;\Nwritten orders; and Mr. 0.
Dialogue: 55,0:10:27.06,0:10:30.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mr. 0? Could that be a code name?!
Dialogue: 55,0:10:30.15,0:10:32.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If so, could he be connected to that
Dialogue: 55,0:10:32.61,0:10:35.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{suspicious swordsman\Nwe caught in Renaisse the other day? - OG}suspicious swordsman\Nwe caught back in Renaisse?{Z}
Dialogue: 55,0:10:36.03,0:10:38.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{With him... Mr. 11?}Connected to him... Mr. 11?
Dialogue: 55,0:10:38.37,0:10:39.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Yeah. Seems like it.  - OG}Yeah, seems like it.
Dialogue: 55,0:10:39.91,0:10:43.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{A criminal organization\Nthat uses numbers for code names... - OG}A criminal organization\Nwith numerical code names{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 55,0:10:43.25,0:10:45.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{and that sends orders via letter\Nto get tasks done. Sound about right? - OG}{that sends written orders. Sound about right? - Z}that sends written orders\Nto carry out missions.{Z/Gaijin/PJ}
Dialogue: 55,0:10:45.83,0:10:47.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sound about right?
Dialogue: 55,0:10:48.09,0:10:51.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Mr. 0? Criminal organization?\NDunno what you're talking about. - OG}{\q2}Mr. 0? Criminal organization? Beats me.
Dialogue: 55,0:10:51.21,0:10:52.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't give me your guesswork. - OG}I've no time for riddles.
Dialogue: 55,0:10:52.67,0:10:57.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Then what was that letter with orders\Nthat we found in your pocket? - OG}Then why did we find a note\Nwith orders on it in your pocket?
Dialogue: 55,0:10:57.43,0:10:59.81,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,I thought I burned that letter!
Dialogue: 55,0:10:59.81,0:11:02.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh! That was... well...
Dialogue: 55,0:11:03.02,0:11:07.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh? But there wasn't\Nanything in your pocket.
Dialogue: 55,0:11:14.15,0:11:15.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Princess Vivi...
Dialogue: 55,0:11:15.57,0:11:19.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's the name of the princess\Nof Alabasta, as I recall. - OG}As I recall, that's the name\Nof the princess of Alabasta.{Z}
Dialogue: 55,0:11:19.24,0:11:22.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{She's currently missing. - OG}However, she's currently missing.
Dialogue: 55,0:11:22.08,0:11:26.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Isn't Alabasta\Nin the middle of coup, too? - OG}Alabasta's in the midst\Nof a coup, correct?
Dialogue: 55,0:11:26.58,0:11:32.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Could this mysterious criminal organization and the Straw Hat Pirates be involved in the uproar somehow? - OG}{\q2}Could this mysterious criminal organization\Nand the Straw Hats somehow be involved?
Dialogue: 55,0:11:32.21,0:11:33.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't know. - OG}Who knows?
Dialogue: 55,0:11:33.71,0:11:38.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But this is the only clue to Straw Hat's whereabouts that we have right now. - OG}But this is the only clue leading us\Nto the Straw Hats right now.
Dialogue: 55,0:11:38.68,0:11:40.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Does that mean we're going to– ? - OG}So, we're going to...
Dialogue: 55,0:11:41.26,0:11:45.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. Contact HQ and get an eternal pose! - OG}Yeah. Contact headquarters\Nand requisition an eternal pose!
Dialogue: 55,0:11:45.60,0:11:46.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 55,0:11:48.10,0:11:53.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Let's pay a visit to Alabasta,\Nthe Country of Sand! - OG}We're going to Alabasta,\Nthe Kingdom of Sand!
Dialogue: 55,0:12:05.25,0:12:11.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We had completely forgotten\Nabout the bounties on our heads!
Dialogue: 55,0:12:11.75,0:12:16.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But I was the reason they came\Nto this island in the first place... - OG}If it weren't for me, they would have\Nnever ventured to this island.
Dialogue: 55,0:12:16.13,0:12:16.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 55,0:12:16.80,0:12:18.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Let's have none of that! - OG}{Don't give me that. - Z}Enough of that.{Westfal}
Dialogue: 55,0:12:18.84,0:12:22.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, Vivi! What're you\Nso down in the dumps for? - OG}{Yeah, Vivi! Why are you\Nso down in the dumps? - Z}Yeah, Vivi! What are you\Nso bummed about?{Westfal}
Dialogue: 55,0:12:22.47,0:12:23.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Want a rice cracker? - OG}Rice cracker?
Dialogue: 55,0:12:23.47,0:12:25.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Where did you get those? - OG}Wait, where'd those come from?
Dialogue: 55,0:12:25.85,0:12:28.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{All right! For now, let's have\Na rice cracker party! - OG}All right! Time for a rice cracker party!
Dialogue: 55,0:12:28.81,0:12:31.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Rice crackers aren't very exciting.
Dialogue: 55,0:12:31.11,0:12:32.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Really? We can even\Nmake toasts with them! - OG}{Then let's make toasts with 'em. - Z}So then, raise a toast with 'em.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 55,0:12:32.82,0:12:35.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,See? Does anyone blame you?
Dialogue: 55,0:12:35.28,0:12:37.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 55,0:12:37.44,0:12:40.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{C'mon! Don't do that! Honestly! - OG}Look! What a waste! Honestly!
Dialogue: 55,0:12:40.78,0:12:43.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Geez! You can't just\Nwaste food like that! - OG}Seriously, you'll just\Nruin the food like that.
Dialogue: 55,0:12:43.95,0:12:47.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?! Give it here!\NWho said you could have mine?!
Dialogue: 55,0:12:47.29,0:12:48.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Give it back! It's mine!
Dialogue: 55,0:12:48.83,0:12:50.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Who says?! - OG}Says who?!
Dialogue: 55,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 55,0:12:52.21,0:12:54.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nothing. Just a bug.
Dialogue: 55,0:12:54.92,0:12:59.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Still, waiting a year for the log to point\Nto the next island is pretty serious stuff... - OG}{Still, it's no joke that the log takes\None year to register the next island. - Z}Still, waiting a year for the log pose\Nto register the next island is no joke.{Westfal}
Dialogue: 55,0:12:59.55,0:13:02.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah! It's definitely\Nno laughing matter! - OG}You're right! It's no laughing matter!
Dialogue: 55,0:13:03.05,0:13:07.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You saved us. We would like\Nto thank you in some way. - OG}You saved us. We would like\Nto repay you in some way.
Dialogue: 55,0:13:09.02,0:13:12.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Oh, in that case,\Nyou old guys can do something about our log! - OG}Oh, in that case,\Nyou old guys should fix our log!
Dialogue: 55,0:13:13.69,0:13:17.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid logs are the only thing\Nwe can't help you with.
Dialogue: 55,0:13:19.70,0:13:23.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nami-san! Vivi-chwan!\NAnd you other bums too! - OG}Nami my sweet! Vivi my love!\NAnd the rest of you bums!
Dialogue: 55,0:13:23.91,0:13:25.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey! Sanji!
Dialogue: 55,0:13:27.12,0:13:30.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're okay! Thank goodness! - OG}You're all safe! Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 55,0:13:30.00,0:13:34.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That jerk suddenly shows up only\Nafter we needed help! - OG}Of course that flake shows up\Nonly after we need him.
Dialogue: 55,0:13:37.09,0:13:38.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What in the hell?! - OG}What the hell?!{Z}
Dialogue: 55,0:13:38.84,0:13:41.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Are you Mr. 3?!
Dialogue: 55,0:13:41.43,0:13:44.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey! How do you know about Mr. 3?
Dialogue: 55,0:13:45.64,0:13:46.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nami-[/i1]san[/i0]! - OG}Nami!
Dialogue: 55,0:13:47.14,0:13:49.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're so titillating! - OG}{You're mighty risqué today! - Z}What a risqué attire!{Westfal}
Dialogue: 55,0:13:49.22,0:13:50.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Feel like getting slugged? - OG}Wanna risk my fist?
Dialogue: 55,0:13:50.98,0:13:52.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now, now, Nami-san. - OG}Allow me, Nami.
Dialogue: 55,0:13:52.98,0:13:55.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You'll catch a cold dressed like that.
Dialogue: 55,0:13:55.48,0:13:56.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Here you are. - OG}Please, wear this.
Dialogue: 55,0:13:56.86,0:13:57.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 55,0:13:58.98,0:14:03.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,All that aside, I just finished talking\Nwith Mr. 0 via transponder snail.
Dialogue: 55,0:14:04.37,0:14:05.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You talked to the boss?!
Dialogue: 55,0:14:05.82,0:14:10.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I found this weird hideout\Nin the jungle, you see.
Dialogue: 55,0:14:10.91,0:14:15.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He seemed to think I was Mr. 3,
Dialogue: 55,0:14:15.67,0:14:19.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,so I told him I eliminated everyone.
Dialogue: 55,0:14:19.80,0:14:22.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So that means he thinks we're dead?! - OG}So he thinks we're dead?!{Westfal}
Dialogue: 55,0:14:22.93,0:14:28.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So we're finally free\Nof people chasing us, but we can't go anywhere! - OG}Even if we've shaken those chasing us,\Nwe still can't go anywhere!
Dialogue: 55,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Can't go anywhere?
Dialogue: 55,0:14:30.14,0:14:32.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Do we still have business\Non this island?
Dialogue: 55,0:14:32.89,0:14:35.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Just after I managed\Nto get a hold of this, too... - OG}I mean, I just got ahold of this, too.
Dialogue: 55,0:14:43.07,0:14:44.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uh? What?
Dialogue: 55,0:14:44.53,0:14:47.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's an eternal pose to Alabasta!
Dialogue: 55,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Hooray!\N– Hooray!
Dialogue: 55,0:14:49.54,0:14:51.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Now we can set sail!
Dialogue: 55,0:14:51.66,0:14:53.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hooray! Way to go, Sanji-[/i1]kun[/i0]! - OG}Hooray! Way to go, Sanji!
Dialogue: 55,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Thank you, Sanji-[/i1]san[/i0]! - OG}Thank you, Sanji!
Dialogue: 55,0:14:58.46,0:15:00.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I was so worried for a moment there! - OG}I'd almost lost hope!
Dialogue: 55,0:15:00.55,0:15:03.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No, no! It was my pleasure!
Dialogue: 55,0:15:03.55,0:15:05.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I could make you so happy!
Dialogue: 55,0:15:06.05,0:15:09.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,All right, everyone!\NLet's have a rice cracker party!
Dialogue: 55,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh no, Luffy!
Dialogue: 55,0:15:11.97,0:15:14.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We only have three left!\NWe can't have a rice cracker party! - OG}{With only three left,\Nwe can't have a party! - Z}It's not much of a party\Nwith only three left!{Westfal}
Dialogue: 55,0:15:14.27,0:15:14.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 55,0:15:15.94,0:15:18.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You know this is no time for that! - OG}All of that can be put on hold!
Dialogue: 55,0:15:18.69,0:15:19.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Captain!
Dialogue: 55,0:15:19.82,0:15:21.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We don't have\Ntime to be lounging around! - OG}We can't waste a single second!
Dialogue: 55,0:15:23.61,0:15:24.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! Hey, you.
Dialogue: 55,0:15:25.95,0:15:28.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You haven't forgotten\Nour hunting contest, I hope!
Dialogue: 55,0:15:29.53,0:15:32.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nope! But I win! - OG}Right! But I'm easily the winner.
Dialogue: 55,0:15:32.04,0:15:34.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I caught a rhino this huge! - OG}I caught a rhino {\i1}this big{\i0}!
Dialogue: 55,0:15:34.12,0:15:35.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A rhino?
Dialogue: 55,0:15:35.75,0:15:37.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I assume you can eat that?! - OG}Is something like that edible?
Dialogue: 55,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 55,0:15:39.84,0:15:41.04,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,A hunting contest?
Dialogue: 55,0:15:41.30,0:15:43.05,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,A hunting contest?
Dialogue: 55,0:15:43.05,0:15:46.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Those words sound familiar somehow.
Dialogue: 55,0:15:46.05,0:15:47.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yes. - OG}Mm-hmm.{Z}
Dialogue: 55,0:15:49.80,0:15:52.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,All right, round old guy\Nand giant old guy!
Dialogue: 55,0:15:52.47,0:15:53.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We're gonna go now! - OG}We're outta here!
Dialogue: 55,0:15:55.56,0:15:59.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Oh, I see. Well, you do seem\Nto be in a hurry. - OG}Is that so? Well, you do\Nseem anxious to leave.
Dialogue: 55,0:15:59.40,0:16:01.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That's too bad,\Nbut we won't stop you.
Dialogue: 55,0:16:01.57,0:16:03.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I hope your homeland is okay. - OG}Best of wishes for your country.
Dialogue: 55,0:16:03.86,0:16:05.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yes! Thank you!
Dialogue: 55,0:16:05.86,0:16:09.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,See ya! Don't die anymore!
Dialogue: 55,0:16:09.95,0:16:12.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Master! I {\i1}will{\i0} visit Elbaph someday!
Dialogue: 55,0:16:13.29,0:16:16.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You'll see. Mine's {\i1}way{\i0}\Nbigger than yours.
Dialogue: 55,0:16:16.08,0:16:17.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You wish!
Dialogue: 55,0:16:19.04,0:16:21.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\Na brave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 55,0:16:25.30,0:16:27.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Our friends are setting sail.
Dialogue: 55,0:16:27.51,0:16:30.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yes. We can't just sit here.
Dialogue: 55,0:16:30.39,0:16:32.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,There's a monster in the western sea.
Dialogue: 55,0:16:33.43,0:16:35.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Dorry! How are your wounds? - OG}Dorry, how are your wounds?
Dialogue: 55,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{These? They won't kill me. - OG}These? I'll live.{Westfal}
Dialogue: 55,0:16:42.73,0:16:45.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This axe and that sword\Nare just about done with. - OG}My axe and your sword\Nare just about finished.{Z/Sil}
Dialogue: 55,0:16:48.74,0:16:49.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Do you have regrets? - OG}{Any regrets? - Z}Second thoughts?{PJ}
Dialogue: 55,0:16:50.20,0:16:54.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I do. This axe fought alongside me\Nfor over 100 years. - OG}{Indeed. This axe has been my partner\Nin battle for well over a century. - Z}{\q2}Of course. This axe has been my partner\Nin battle for well over a century.{Z/PJ}
Dialogue: 55,0:16:54.45,0:16:55.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But, - OG}However,
Dialogue: 55,0:16:55.74,0:16:58.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{if it's for them, it's worth it! - OG}if it's to help them out,\Nthen it's worth it!
Dialogue: 55,0:16:59.21,0:17:01.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Then it's decided... - OG}That settles it.
Dialogue: 55,0:17:10.72,0:17:13.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{See?! Mine's far huger than yours! - OG}See?! Mine's much bigger than yours!
Dialogue: 55,0:17:13.72,0:17:15.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Look closer! My lizard's bigger! - OG}Look closer! My lizard's enormous!
Dialogue: 55,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Are you blind or something?!
Dialogue: 55,0:17:18.64,0:17:21.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{My rhino's way bigger! - OG}My rhino's much more humongous!
Dialogue: 55,0:17:21.73,0:17:23.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It doesn't really matter!\NThey both look yummy! - OG}{It doesn't matter!\NThey both look delicious! - Z}Either way, they both look yummy!{Z/Westfal}
Dialogue: 55,0:17:24.23,0:17:25.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You shut up and mind your own business! - OG}– Mind your own business!\N– Mind your own business!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 55,0:17:25.73,0:17:26.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 55,0:17:26.23,0:17:30.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Look! Mine's bigger!\N– No, mine is!
Dialogue: 55,0:17:30.53,0:17:32.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{How long are you\Ngonna keep at that? - OG}How long do you two\Nplan to keep at it?
Dialogue: 55,0:17:33.37,0:17:38.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We don't need all of it, so cut up\Nwhat we do need so we can set sail! - OG}{Just cut them up and stow\Nwhat we can so we can set sail! - Z}Just butcher them and load what fits\Nso we can set sail!{Westfal}
Dialogue: 55,0:17:38.12,0:17:39.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yes, Nami-[/i1]san[/i0]! - OG}Yes, Nami!
Dialogue: 55,0:17:40.12,0:17:43.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, Usopp! I'm clearly\Nthe winner, right?!
Dialogue: 55,0:17:43.25,0:17:45.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Huh? I don't really care.
Dialogue: 55,0:17:45.13,0:17:46.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Can't you call it a tie? - OG}Can't you call it a draw?
Dialogue: 55,0:17:47.17,0:17:49.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There are no ties in a challenge! - OG}There are no draws in a challenge!
Dialogue: 55,0:17:49.01,0:17:50.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hurry it up! - OG}Move your asses!
Dialogue: 55,0:17:51.68,0:17:53.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 55,0:17:58.10,0:18:00.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Set sail!
Dialogue: 55,0:18:04.77,0:18:08.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They said going straight will take us\Nto the western end of the island.
Dialogue: 55,0:18:08.36,0:18:11.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey. Couldn't you have\Ngotten any more meat on board? - OG}Hey. Is this all the meat\Nwe could carry?
Dialogue: 55,0:18:11.11,0:18:14.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, right! Don't be stupid! We\Ncan't preserve any more than that. - OG}Use your head! We can't\Npreserve any more than this.
Dialogue: 55,0:18:14.20,0:18:16.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Do you {\i1}want{\i0} to sink the ship?!
Dialogue: 55,0:18:22.46,0:18:26.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Look, it's the old guys!\NThey came to see us off!
Dialogue: 55,0:18:30.96,0:18:33.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ahead is a great obstacle...
Dialogue: 55,0:18:34.30,0:18:38.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,...that prevents people who come\Nto this island from reaching the next.
Dialogue: 55,0:18:41.06,0:18:45.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You fought desperately\Nto protect our pride.{Used as flashback in Enies Lobby 05 @17:35}
Dialogue: 55,0:18:45.31,0:18:48.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{As such, no matter what\Nmanner of enemy there may be... - OG}Therefore, no matter the enemy\Nthat may rear its head...
Dialogue: 55,0:18:52.44,0:18:55.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{we will not let them\Ndestroy your pride, friends! - OG}...we will keep it from\Ntrampling {\i1}your{\i0} pride, friends!
Dialogue: 55,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Have faith in us,\Nand continue straight ahead! - OG}Have faith and keep straight!
Dialogue: 55,0:18:59.91,0:19:02.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Straight ahead,\Nno matter what happens! - OG}No matter what happens,\Nsail straight ahead!
Dialogue: 55,0:19:04.04,0:19:05.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 55,0:19:06.25,0:19:07.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 55,0:19:08.21,0:19:09.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Wh-What do you got? - OG}Wh-What's the word?
Dialogue: 55,0:19:10.00,0:19:12.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We'll sail straight ahead,\Nno matter what happens!
Dialogue: 55,0:19:20.26,0:19:21.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This is goodbye! - OG}We bid you farewell!
Dialogue: 55,0:19:21.64,0:19:23.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Let us meet again someday.{Used as flashback in Enies Lobby 05 @17:53}
Dialogue: 55,0:19:23.39,0:19:24.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Without fail.
Dialogue: 55,0:19:24.85,0:19:25.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Up ahead! - OG}Look! Ahead!
Dialogue: 55,0:19:32.65,0:19:34.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,There you are, Island Gorger!
Dialogue: 55,0:19:34.70,0:19:38.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You will open the path,\Nin the name of Elbaph! - OG}You {\i1}will{\i0} make way,\Nlest the pride of Elbaph fail us.
Dialogue: 55,0:20:01.05,0:20:01.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 55,0:20:01.93,0:20:03.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Something's appeared!
Dialogue: 55,0:20:05.64,0:20:08.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What's this guy? A goldfish? - OG}What {\i1}is{\i0} this guy? A goldfish?
Dialogue: 55,0:20:09.10,0:20:11.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A g-giant goldfish?!
Dialogue: 55,0:20:11.06,0:20:13.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why does that sound familiar?!
Dialogue: 55,0:20:13.23,0:20:16.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Work the rudder! Hurry!\NWe're gonna get eaten!
Dialogue: 55,0:20:16.24,0:20:18.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usopp! Hurry!
Dialogue: 55,0:20:18.11,0:20:19.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I... I can't!
Dialogue: 55,0:20:19.20,0:20:22.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Go straight ahead! R-Right, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 55,0:20:23.49,0:20:24.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 55,0:20:30.75,0:20:34.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't be stupid! This won't be\Nlike what happened with Laboon! - OG}{\q2}Don't be stupid! Laboon was one thing,\Nbut this is nothing like him!
Dialogue: 55,0:20:35.01,0:20:37.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I know. Calm down. - OG}I know. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 55,0:20:37.72,0:20:39.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Here, I'll let you have the last rice cracker. - OG}Here, have the last rice cracker.
Dialogue: 55,0:20:40.05,0:20:41.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I don't want it!
Dialogue: 55,0:20:41.34,0:20:44.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If we don't turn\Nthe ship, we're gonna be...
Dialogue: 55,0:20:46.06,0:20:47.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Just give it up, Nami.
Dialogue: 55,0:20:52.02,0:20:55.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Luffy! We can trust those guys, I hope! - OG}Luffy! We can trust\Nthose guys, I take it?!
Dialogue: 55,0:20:55.44,0:20:56.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 55,0:20:56.03,0:20:59.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Are you crazy?! Are we really\Ngoing straight into that beast?! - OG}Are you crazy?! Are we really\Nsailing straight into that beast?!
Dialogue: 55,0:20:59.86,0:21:02.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No! We're too late now! - OG}Oh no! There's no turning back now!
Dialogue: 55,0:21:11.46,0:21:14.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You've really grown a lot, Island Gorger! - OG}You've really grown, Island Gorger!
Dialogue: 55,0:21:14.21,0:21:15.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You filthy monster goldfish! - OG}You monstrous goldfish!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 55,0:21:16.59,0:21:19.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{His size isn't his only surprise. - OG}His size isn't the only surprising thing.
Dialogue: 55,0:21:19.84,0:21:22.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There's also the size\Nand length of the dung he produces - OG}This monster eats islands whole
Dialogue: 55,0:21:22.76,0:21:25.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{after devouring any islands nearby. - OG}and leaves behind\Ncolossal lengths of dung.
Dialogue: 55,0:21:25.76,0:21:26.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I recall - OG}As I recall,
Dialogue: 55,0:21:26.77,0:21:29.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{a giant piece of dung named Nihiland. - OG}one such floating dung heap\Nwas named Nihiland.
Dialogue: 55,0:21:32.35,0:21:36.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And that we landed on it long ago,\Nthinking it was actual land! - OG}{And to think we actually landed on it long ago, mistaking it for an island! - Z}We actually landed on it long ago,\Nmistaking it for an island!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 55,0:21:36.82,0:21:39.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This is a nostalgic day of adventure! - OG}Today makes me\Nnostalgic for adventure!
Dialogue: 55,0:21:39.32,0:21:42.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{As I look at them,\NI'm reminded of the old days! - OG}As I watch that crew,\NI'm reminded of the old days!
Dialogue: 55,0:21:46.79,0:21:51.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The only thing we can't penetrate\Nis the bloodstained snake!
Dialogue: 55,0:21:52.54,0:21:56.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Observe, the most powerful giant\Nspear, as passed down in Elbaph! - OG}Behold! The mighty, legendary spear\Nas taught only to those from Elbaph!
Dialogue: 55,0:22:01.59,0:22:03.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Straight ahead! Straight ahead!
Dialogue: 55,0:22:04.05,0:22:06.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What are you talking about?!\NWe've already been eaten! - OG}What's the point?!\NWe've already been eaten!
Dialogue: 55,0:22:07.18,0:22:09.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Straight ahead! Straight ahead!
Dialogue: 55,0:22:17.57,0:22:19.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}– Dominion!\N– Dominion!
Dialogue: 55,0:22:24.32,0:22:26.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\t(19,978,\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}{We're flying out of it! - OG}We're flying right out of it!{Used as flashback in Enies Lobby 25 @12:50}
Dialogue: 55,0:22:34.29,0:22:37.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Don't look back!\NWe're going straight ahead!
Dialogue: 55,0:22:40.88,0:22:44.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's huge! So huge!
Dialogue: 55,0:22:44.72,0:22:48.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They cut... the very sea itself...
Dialogue: 55,0:22:48.35,0:22:52.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is the strength of Elbaph warriors!
Dialogue: 55,0:22:53.23,0:22:55.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Incredible! - OG}It's incredible!
Dialogue: 55,0:23:08.33,0:23:09.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Friends!\N– Friends!
Dialogue: 55,0:23:14.79,0:23:16.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Now go!\N– Now go!
Dialogue: 55,0:23:27.43,0:23:29.47,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,{Long ago, - OG}Long ago,
Dialogue: 55,0:23:29.47,0:23:33.77,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,{there were a group of ruffians on the sea... - OG}{\q2}there was a group of ruffians on the sea\Nknown as the Giant Warrior Pirates.
Dialogue: 55,0:23:34.18,0:23:37.06,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,{The two pirate bosses, - OG}The two pirate chiefs,{Z}
Dialogue: 55,0:23:37.06,0:23:40.82,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,Brogy the Red Ogre\Nand Dorry the Blue Ogre,
Dialogue: 55,0:23:40.82,0:23:42.23,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,{were exceptionally strong. - OG}stood unrivaled in might.
Dialogue: 55,0:23:43.40,0:23:47.20,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,{Since ordinary people no longer stood a chance against them, they were mostly left unchecked. - OG}{Since ordinary people did not\Nstand a chance against them, they were left mostly unchecked. - Z}Ordinary people no longer posed\Na threat to them and steered clear.{Z}
Dialogue: 55,0:23:47.20,0:23:53.08,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,{But they say that the one who put an end to their attacks... - OG}But they say that the one\Nwho finally put an end to their run...
Dialogue: 55,0:23:53.62,0:23:57.25,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,{was a single little girl. - OG}was a mere little girl.
Dialogue: 55,0:24:00.25,0:24:03.38,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{You see what\Nour bosses caught today?! - OG}You see what\Nour chiefs caught today?!{Z}
Dialogue: 55,0:24:03.38,0:24:08.43,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah! It's stuck in my mind!\NMy excitement won't stop! - OG}Yeah! It's all I can think about!\NWhat a day to be alive!
Dialogue: 55,0:24:08.43,0:24:13.77,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Each one of them bagged\Nan insanely huge sea king, after all!{Used as flashback in Enies Lobby 05 @13:40}
Dialogue: 55,0:24:14.27,0:24:17.31,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Even though we're Elbaph giants,
Dialogue: 55,0:24:17.31,0:24:22.61,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{nobody can take down those jumbo-sized beasts, except for our bosses! - OG}nobody but the chiefs can take down\Nthose jumbo-sized monsters!
Dialogue: 55,0:24:22.61,0:24:23.98,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Right, men?!
Dialogue: 55,0:24:24.73,0:24:25.49,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 55,0:24:25.49,0:24:27.28,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,You got that right!
Dialogue: 55,0:24:30.37,0:24:34.08,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Those ones were definitely\Nthe biggest ones... - OG}These ones are\Ndefinitely our biggest yet!{Z/Sil}
Dialogue: 55,0:24:36.45,0:24:39.00,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah! The biggest ones we've ever caught! - OG}Yeah! Bigger than anything\Nwe've ever caught!
Dialogue: 55,0:24:41.63,0:24:43.80,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,So which one was bigger?
Dialogue: 55,0:24:46.09,0:24:46.92,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Which...
Dialogue: 55,0:24:46.92,0:24:48.05,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,...one?
Dialogue: 55,0:24:49.18,0:24:51.22,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Who won the hunting contest?
Dialogue: 55,0:24:56.06,0:24:59.89,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Look, Brogy! Mine is slightly bigger!
Dialogue: 55,0:24:59.89,0:25:03.36,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{You wish! Mine's a whole 3 centimeters bigger! - OG}Keep dreaming! Mine's a whole\Nthree centimeters longer!
Dialogue: 55,0:25:03.36,0:25:04.57,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 55,0:25:04.57,0:25:05.61,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{What's your problem?! - OG}What?!
Dialogue: 55,0:25:05.61,0:25:08.65,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Bosses! Please stop! - OG}Chiefs! Please stop!{Z}
Dialogue: 55,0:25:16.24,0:25:22.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, Brogy, there's one thing\NI can't seem to remember.
Dialogue: 55,0:25:22.13,0:25:24.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No, actually, that goes for me, too.
Dialogue: 55,0:25:28.47,0:25:29.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Middle Mountain! - OG}The central mountain!
Dialogue: 55,0:25:30.43,0:25:31.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No matter! - OG}No need to dwell on it!
Dialogue: 55,0:25:31.76,0:25:34.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Let's just finish this now! - OG}Let's settle this, once and for all!
Dialogue: 55,0:25:34.55,0:25:35.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah! - OG}You're right!
Dialogue: 55,0:25:35.85,0:25:37.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We can think\Nthings through after that! - OG}We'll sort things out afterward!
